description: TRX_DLL files may appear as ONINTL.DLL.trx_dll or STINTL.DLL.trx_dll , which are produced when errors are encountered. This may result in decreased system response time or the computer freezing or crashing. TRX_DLL errors can result from viruses and malicious spyware .

common_filenames.description: ENVELOPR.DLL.trx_dll - Windows system file referenced when executing DLL files that identifies what libraries need to be loaded into memory.
